===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Unclear. Generally considered to be unrelated to {{zh-l|*告}} in its original form.

The bronze script forms are identified by 漢語多功能字庫 as being {{Han compound|辵|屮|口|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|c3=s|t1=to walk|tr2=sʰuːʔ}} – “to go, to arrive”.

''{{w|Shuowen}}'' incorrectly identifies it as a {{Han compound|辵|alt1=辶|告|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=to walk}}.

